{"tid":1322521,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"真（點）輸出香港革命精神","createTime":"2019-07-16T03:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T09:52:52.000Z","uid":279644,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2b8f90a38ce9bb5e7a0e1044be1b9a668e67b612","tid":1322521,"uid":279644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:15:18.000Z","msg":"自從香蕉糖出現咗係台灣後，<br />\n同台灣朋友傾開計，<br />\n佢話佢都<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>好想擁有香蕉糖</strong></span><br />\n樓主就心血來潮思如潮湧靈感一發諗到：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">不如將香蕉糖Print成Postcard寄過去啦！</span></span></strong></span><br />\n等郵差叔叔可以帶住香蕉糖<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>穿洋過海，踏遍天涯</strong></span>。<br />\n所以樓主係到呼籲大家，<br />\n可以選擇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">富有香港特色嘅文宣</span></span></strong><br />\n長輩圖也好，香蕉糖也好，純文字也好<br />\n不單可以印街招<br />\n重可以拎去<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">印Postcard</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">寄遍世界各地，<br />\n輸出香港精神！</span></span></strong><br />\n**溫馨提示：寄往外語地區記得做好翻譯"},{"pid":"81c788dfcab678fb2da8016e177696f8701dfe96","tid":1322521,"uid":153598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:38:41.000Z","msg":"環球隻抽"},{"pid":"62fad8428dda1bc8e83dec201b9d07d1e2870e2d","tid":1322521,"uid":281108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:49:49.000Z","msg":"正喎 平時最鍾意寫postcard!"},{"pid":"53fbd93acc9eac5e07cdc6de12cbdf32fb9e70d5","tid":1322521,"uid":279644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:52:52.000Z","msg":"push"}]}